stringStats.value: Many claimed these were less some form of Snow Golem and more strange creatures drawn from Ispar into Dereth. Appearing during the winter months, many Snowmen added a festive spirit to the season; in fact, it was rumored that one hidden Snowman vendor even sold unique and frosty food. Other Snowmen, however, proved less than jolly, demonstrating just how much damage a hurled ball of ice could cause.
